headline: 3 Healthcare Stocks to Buy for a 2025 Rebound
summary: Healthcare stocks have gotten crushed in 2024, and next year doesn’t look much better.  Recent developments, including a bipartisan bill calling for insurers to separate from their pharmacy benefit management units, or PBMs, has caused pain, but the sector has been unloved for most of the last 11 months and change.
